Uses of Package
net.sf.jclal.core

  • Packages that use net.sf.jclal.core 
    Package Description
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.algorithm
    The package contains the active learning algorithm.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.batchmode
    The package contains the batch mode strategies to use by a scenario and query strategy.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy
    The package contains the multilabel query strategies.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy.research  
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy.research.batchmode  
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy.research.genetic  
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.oracle
    The package contains implementations of Oracles.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.querystrategy
    The package contains the class that represents an abstract query strategies.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.scenario
    The package contains the AL scenarios.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.singlelabel.querystrategy
    The package contains the query strategies for single label data.
    net.sf.jclal.activelearning.stopcriterion
    The package contains stop criterion implementations for AL process.
    net.sf.jclal.classifier
    The package contains the wrapper classifiers.
    net.sf.jclal.core
    The package contains the core of the framework.
    net.sf.jclal.dataset
    The package contains the bridge classes to represent a dataset.
    net.sf.jclal.evaluation.measure
    The package contains the evaluation measures of the framework.
    net.sf.jclal.evaluation.method
    The package contains the evaluation methods
    net.sf.jclal.experiment
    The package contains the classes to run an experiment.
    net.sf.jclal.gui.view.components.chart
    The package contains a component to visualize the experiment's results.
    net.sf.jclal.listener
    The package contains a set of listeners
    net.sf.jclal.sampling
    The package contains the sampling's class used to construct the initial labeled set.
    net.sf.jclal.sampling.supervised
    The package contains the sampling's class used to construct the initial labeled set.
    net.sf.jclal.util.dataset
    The package contains a collection of utility classes to handle the datasets.
    net.sf.jclal.util.mail
    The package contains utility classes to send an email.
    net.sf.jclal.util.random
    The package contains random generators and related classes.
    net.sf.jclal.util.xml
    The package contains the classes used to construct a xml configuration file.
